#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.45"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.45:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.45:0.2"
msgid "5. Akkosavagga "
msgstr "5. Abuse "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.45:0.3"
msgid "45. Rājantepurappavesanasutta "
msgstr "45. Entering a Royal Harem "

# NOTE: I use harem as more specific than the vague euphemism “inner palace”. Interestingly enough, though, the roots of the word harem is “forbidden”, i.e. taboo. Access to the harem was strcitly forbidden in Islamic courts. Here, though, it seems that it was considered normal for even a monk to enter the harem, and the reasons for not doing so are entirely practical, not magical or spiritual.
#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
msgctxt "an10.45:0.4"
msgid "“Dasayime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā rājantepurappavesane. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are ten drawbacks to entering a royal harem. "

msgctxt "an10.45:0.5"
msgid "Katame dasa? "
msgstr "What ten? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.45:0.6"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, rājā mahesiyā saddhiṃ nisinno hoti. "
msgstr "Firstly, a king is sitting with his chief queen "

msgctxt "an10.45:0.7"
msgid "Tatra bhikkhu pavisati. "
msgstr "when a monk enters. "

msgctxt "an10.45:0.8"
msgid "Mahesī vā bhikkhuṃ disvā sitaṃ pātukaroti, bhikkhu vā mahesiṃ disvā sitaṃ pātukaroti. "
msgstr "When the queen sees the monk she smiles, or when the monk sees the queen he smiles. "

msgctxt "an10.45:0.9"
msgid "Tattha rañño evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "So the king thinks: "

msgctxt "an10.45:0.10"
msgid "‘addhā imesaṃ kataṃ vā karissanti vā’ti. "
msgstr "‘They’ve done it for sure, or they will do it.’ "

msgctxt "an10.45:0.11"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo ādīnavo rājantepurappavesane. (1) "
msgstr "This is the first drawback of entering a royal harem. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.82, sc2
msgctxt "an10.45:2.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, rājā bahukicco bahukaraṇīyo aññataraṃ itthiṃ gantvā na sarati: "
msgstr "Furthermore, a king has many duties, and much to do. He has sex with one of the women but doesn’t remember. "

msgctxt "an10.45:2.2"
msgid "‘sā tena gabbhaṃ gaṇhāti’. "
msgstr "She gets pregnant from that. "

msgctxt "an10.45:2.3"
msgid "Tattha rañño evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "So the king thinks: "

msgctxt "an10.45:2.4"
msgid "‘na kho idha añño koci pavisati, aññatra pabbajitena. "
msgstr "‘No-one else has entered here, except for that monk. "

msgctxt "an10.45:2.5"
msgid "Siyā nu kho pabbajitassa kamman’ti. "
msgstr "Could this be the monk’s doing?’ "

msgctxt "an10.45:2.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo ādīnavo rājantepurappavesane. (2) "
msgstr "This is the second drawback of entering a royal harem. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an10.45:3.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, rañño antepure aññataraṃ ratanaṃ nassati. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a gem is lost somewhere in the royal harem. "

msgctxt "an10.45:3.2"
msgid "Tattha rañño evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "So the king thinks: "

msgctxt "an10.45:3.3"
msgid "‘na kho idha añño koci pavisati, aññatra pabbajitena. "
msgstr "‘No-one else has entered here, except for that monk. "

msgctxt "an10.45:3.4"
msgid "Siyā nu kho pabbajitassa kamman’ti. "
msgstr "Could this be the monk’s doing?’ "

msgctxt "an10.45:3.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo ādīnavo rājantepurappavesane. (3) "
msgstr "This is the third drawback of entering a royal harem. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an10.45:4.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, rañño antepure abbhantarā guyhamantā bahiddhā sambhedaṃ gacchanti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, secret deliberations in the royal harem are leaked outside. "

msgctxt "an10.45:4.2"
msgid "Tattha rañño evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "So the king thinks: "

msgctxt "an10.45:4.3"
msgid "‘na kho idha añño koci pavisati, aññatra pabbajitena. "
msgstr "‘No-one else has entered here, except for that monk. "

msgctxt "an10.45:4.4"
msgid "Siyā nu kho pabbajitassa kamman’ti. "
msgstr "Could this be the monk’s doing?’ "

msgctxt "an10.45:4.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho ādīnavo rājantepurappavesane. (4) "
msgstr "This is the fourth drawback of entering a royal harem. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an10.45:5.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, rañño antepure pitā vā puttaṃ pattheti putto vā pitaraṃ pattheti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, in a royal harem, a father longs for their son, or a son longs for his father. "

msgctxt "an10.45:5.2"
msgid "Tesaṃ evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "They think: "

msgctxt "an10.45:5.3"
msgid "‘na kho idha añño koci pavisati, aññatra pabbajitena. "
msgstr "‘No-one else has entered here, except for that monk. "

msgctxt "an10.45:5.4"
msgid "Siyā nu kho pabbajitassa kamman’ti. "
msgstr "Could this be the monk’s doing?’ "

msgctxt "an10.45:5.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, pañcamo ādīnavo rājantepurappavesane. (5) "
msgstr "This is the fifth drawback of entering a royal harem. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an10.45:6.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, rājā nīcaṭṭhāniyaṃ ucce ṭhāne ṭhapeti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, the king promotes someone to a higher position. "

msgctxt "an10.45:6.2"
msgid "Yesaṃ taṃ amanāpaṃ tesaṃ evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "Those who are upset by this think: "

msgctxt "an10.45:6.3"
msgid "‘rājā kho pabbajitena saṃsaṭṭho. "
msgstr "‘The king is close to that monk. "

msgctxt "an10.45:6.4"
msgid "Siyā nu kho pabbajitassa kamman’ti. "
msgstr "Could this be the monk’s doing?’ "

msgctxt "an10.45:6.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, chaṭṭho ādīnavo rājantepurappavesane. (6) "
msgstr "This is the sixth drawback of entering a royal harem. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an10.45:7.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, rājā uccaṭṭhāniyaṃ nīce ṭhāne ṭhapeti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, the king demotes someone to a lower position. "

msgctxt "an10.45:7.2"
msgid "Yesaṃ taṃ amanāpaṃ tesaṃ evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "Those who are upset by this think: "

msgctxt "an10.45:7.3"
msgid "‘rājā kho pabbajitena saṃsaṭṭho. "
msgstr "‘The king is close to that monk. "

msgctxt "an10.45:7.4"
msgid "Siyā nu kho pabbajitassa kamman’ti. "
msgstr "Could this be the monk’s doing?’ "

msgctxt "an10.45:7.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, sattamo ādīnavo rājantepurappavesane. (7) "
msgstr "This is the seventh drawback of entering a royal harem. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an10.45:8.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, rājā akāle senaṃ uyyojeti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, the king dispatches the army at the wrong time. "

msgctxt "an10.45:8.2"
msgid "Yesaṃ taṃ amanāpaṃ tesaṃ evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "Those who are upset by this think: "

msgctxt "an10.45:8.3"
msgid "‘rājā kho pabbajitena saṃsaṭṭho. "
msgstr "‘The king is close to that monk. "

msgctxt "an10.45:8.4"
msgid "Siyā nu kho pabbajitassa kamman’ti. "
msgstr "Could this be the monk’s doing?’ "

msgctxt "an10.45:8.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, aṭṭhamo ādīnavo rājantepurappavesane. (8) "
msgstr "This is the eighth drawback of entering a royal harem. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.83, sc9
msgctxt "an10.45:9.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, rājā kāle senaṃ uyyojetvā antarāmaggato nivattāpeti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, the king dispatches the army at the right time, but orders it to turn back while still on the road. "

msgctxt "an10.45:9.2"
msgid "Yesaṃ taṃ amanāpaṃ tesaṃ evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "Those who are upset by this think: "

msgctxt "an10.45:9.3"
msgid "‘rājā kho pabbajitena saṃsaṭṭho. "
msgstr "‘The king is close to that monk. "

msgctxt "an10.45:9.4"
msgid "Siyā nu kho pabbajitassa kamman’ti. "
msgstr "Could this be the monk’s doing?’ "

msgctxt "an10.45:9.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, navamo ādīnavo rājantepurappavesane. (9) "
msgstr "This is the ninth drawback of entering a royal harem. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an10.45:10.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, rañño antepuraṃ hatthisammaddaṃ assasammaddaṃ rathasammaddaṃ rajanīyāni rūpasaddagandharasaphoṭṭhabbāni, yāni na pabbajitassa sāruppāni. "
msgstr "Furthermore, in the royal harem there is a trampling of elephants, horses, and chariots, as well as arousing sights, sounds, smells, tastes, and touches that do not befit a monk. "

msgctxt "an10.45:10.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dasamo ādīnavo rājantepurappavesane. "
msgstr "This is the tenth drawback of entering a royal harem. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.45:10.3"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, dasa ādīnavā rājantepurappavesane”ti. (10) "
msgstr "These are the ten drawbacks of entering a royal harem.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.45:10.4"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
